# ReMindRAG Reproducibility Report

**Date:** 2026-03-07 | **Test Suite:** 17/17 passed | **Docker:** Builds and runs successfully

---

## Phase 1 -- Repository Understanding

### Structure Summary

```
ReMindRAG/
+-- ReMindRag/              # Core library
|   +-- llms/               # LLM agent interface (OpenAI API)
|   +-- embeddings/         # HuggingFace sentence-transformers
|   +-- chunking/           # Naive + Meta chunking strategies
|   +-- database/           # ChromaDB vector store + KG extraction
|   +-- generator/          # RAG response generation + path finding
|   +-- kg/                 # Knowledge graph construction
|   +-- webui/              # Flask-based web interface
|   +-- utils/              # Logging, decorators
+-- eval/                   # LooGLE + HotpotQA evaluation scripts
+-- example/                # Minimal usage example
+-- Dockerfile              # Multi-stage deterministic build
+-- requirements.txt        # Pinned dependencies (146 packages)
+-- test_reproducibility.py # Automated 17-test audit suite
+-- repro_test.py           # Quick smoke test with mock agents
```

### Python Version

**Required:** 3.13.2 (specified in README)

### Dependencies

146 packages pinned in [requirements.txt](file:///c:/Users/mtuan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/ReMindRAG/requirements.txt). Key ones:

| Package | Version | Purpose |
|---------|---------|---------|
| torch | 2.6.0+cu126 | Deep learning framework |
| transformers | 4.49.0 | HuggingFace model loading |
| sentence-transformers | 4.0.2 | Embedding models |
| chromadb | 0.6.3 | Vector database |
| openai | 1.65.5 | LLM API client |
| networkx | 3.4.2 | Knowledge graph |
| flask | 3.1.0 | WebUI |
| nltk | 3.9.1 | Sentence tokenization |

### Missing Files / Artifacts Identified

| Item | Status |
|------|--------|
| [api_key.json](file:///c:/Users/mtuan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/ReMindRAG/api_key.json) | User must create (contains OpenAI credentials) |
| `model_cache/` | Auto-downloaded from HuggingFace on first run |
| `eval/dataset_cache/LooGLE-rewrite-data/` | Must download from [Google Drive](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1gv7rfiuMEVNMABttp6SZLzSJR-sZNfU5/view?usp=sharing) |

