## Phase 6 -- Determinism & Result Verification

### Random Seeds

| Component | Status |
|-----------|--------|
| `random.seed()` | Fixed via `set_seed(42)` in `eval_LooGLE.py` |
| `np.random.seed()` | Fixed via `set_seed(42)` |
| `torch.manual_seed()` | Fixed via `set_seed(42)` |
| `torch.cuda.manual_seed_all()` | Fixed (if GPU available) |
| `cudnn.deterministic` | Set to `True` |
| `cudnn.benchmark` | Set to `False` |

### Seed CLI Control

```shell
python eval/eval_LooGLE.py --seed 42 --title_index 0 --data_type longdep_qa --question_type origin
```

### Non-Determinism Sources (Cannot Fix)

| Source | Impact |
|--------|--------|
| OpenAI API responses | `temperature=0` reduces but does not eliminate variance |
| Model version updates | OpenAI may update `gpt-4o-mini` weights silently |
| HuggingFace model revisions | `nomic-embed-text-v2-moe` may receive updates |

### Hyperparameter Logging

Key parameters visible in eval script CLI args:
- `--model_name` (backbone LLM)
- `--judge_model_name` (evaluation judge LLM)  
- `--seed` (random seed)
- `edge_weight_coefficient=0.1`, `strong_connection_threshold=0.5` (hardcoded in eval scripts)

