## Phase 7 -- Automated Debugging (Issues Found & Fixed)

| # | Severity | Issue | Fix |
|---|----------|-------|-----|
| 1 | CRITICAL | `requirements_repro.txt` UTF-16 encoded | Re-encoded to UTF-8 |
| 2 | CRITICAL | Missing `--extra-index-url` in README | Documented in install steps |
| 3 | CRITICAL | `model_cache/` dir never created | `os.makedirs(exist_ok=True)` |
| 4 | CRITICAL | `chroma_data/` dir never created | `os.makedirs(exist_ok=True)` |
| 5 | CRITICAL | `logs/` dir never created | `os.makedirs(exist_ok=True)` |
| 6 | CRITICAL | WebUI `temp/` dir never created | `os.makedirs(exist_ok=True)` |
| 7 | HIGH | Judge model hardcoded to `gpt-4o` | Added `--judge_model_name` arg |
| 8 | HIGH | LooGLE dataset provenance undocumented | Documented in README |
| 9 | HIGH | `start_LooGLE.py` no resume guard | Added skip logic for completed tests |
| 10 | HIGH | `daatabase_description` typo | Fixed in rag_main.py + preprocess.py |
| 11 | MEDIUM | String path concatenation | Replaced with `os.path.join` |
| 12 | MEDIUM | CWD-dependent path resolution | `__file__`-relative via EVAL_DIR |
| 13 | MEDIUM | `trust_remote_code` undocumented | Noted in README |
| 14 | MEDIUM | HF token ephemeral only | Added `huggingface-cli login` docs |

