## Phase 8 -- Paper-to-Code Alignment

### Core Components Implemented

| Paper Component | Code Location | Status |
|----------------|---------------|--------|
| Knowledge Graph construction | `ReMindRag/kg/` | Implemented |
| LLM-guided graph traversal | `ReMindRag/generator/pathfinder.py` | Implemented |
| Edge weight reinforcement/punishment | `ReMindRag/database/chromaDB.py` (`enhance_edge_weight`, `punish_edge_weight`) | Implemented |
| Chunk-level entity extraction | `ReMindRag/database/data_extract.py` | Implemented |
| ChromaDB vector storage | `ReMindRag/database/chromaDB.py` | Implemented |
| LooGLE evaluation | `eval/eval_LooGLE.py` | Implemented |
| HotpotQA evaluation | `eval/eval_Hotpot.py` | Implemented |

### Baselines

No baseline implementations included -- the repo only contains the ReMindRAG method itself.

### Hyperparameters Documented

| Parameter | Value | Location |
|-----------|-------|----------|
| `edge_weight_coefficient` | 0.1 | `eval_LooGLE.py:L143` |
| `strong_connection_threshold` | 0.5 | `eval_LooGLE.py:L144` |
| `max_token_length` (chunker) | 750 | `eval_LooGLE.py:L94` |
| `temperature` (LLM) | 0 | `openai_api.py:L37` |
| `chunk_summary_threshold` | 5 (default) | `rag_main.py:L23` |

